      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready for a rewarding project with this diamond in the rough! While it definitely needs some mechanical attention and bodywork to get back to its best, it's a fantastic opportunity for a savvy buyer to build some serious equity. If you're looking for an affordable entry point and aren't afraid of a little hard work, this is the perfect canvas for your next restoration!",
