    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, essentially indistinguishable from a new car on the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no chips, scratches, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state, with the leather seating and trim showing zero signs of wear and still carrying that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive care. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the production line.",
