    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's eager to get back on the road! This car is in fair condition, offering a solid and reliable driving experience while showing some honest character from its years of service. It has some visible wear and tear both inside and out, but it's a great, budget-friendly option for anyone looking for a functional vehicle with plenty of life left in it!",
