    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to be listing this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of every little detail, so you won't find a single scratch or blemish anywhere. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new and ready for some fun, this is the one for you. I'd love to see it go to a great home, so feel free to reach out!",
      "price": 43500.0,
