    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) is a preserved example of high-revving precision. Powered by the legendary F22C1 naturally aspirated inline-four, it features a 2.2L displacement with a revised powerband and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain remains factory-spec, utilizing the crisp 6-speed short-throw manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. The chassis integrity is flawless, retaining the rigidity of the original X-bone frame and the surgical response of the four-wheel double-wishbone suspension. Every VIN tag is present, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the undercarriage shows zero oxidation or fluid seepage. A true collector-grade specimen for the purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
